### Feature 1: Query Autocorrect

Auto-correct typos in user queries before sending to RAG pipeline. Shows the corrected query to the user with a "Did you mean?" prompt.

#### [NEW] [autocorrect_engine.py](file:///b:/GenAI_Project/core/autocorrect_engine.py)

```python
# Uses `autocorrect` library (offline, fast)
# Pipeline: raw query → spell check → show diff if changed → use corrected
