1. **Phase 1 — Foundation**: Feature 8 (UI overhaul) — this changes the layout that all other features plug into
2. **Phase 2 — Core Fixes**: Feature 9 (fix summarize) + Feature 2 (multi-format upload)
3. **Phase 3 — RAG Enhancements**: Feature 1 (autocorrect) + Feature 3 (adaptive chunking) + Feature 6 (guardrails)
4. **Phase 4 — UX Improvements**: Feature 4 (dual panel) + Feature 10 (suggested questions) + Feature 5 (system monitor)
5. **Phase 5 — Internationalization**: Feature 7 (live translation)
6. **Phase 6 — Multi-User**: Feature 11 (auth) + Feature 12 (query visibility) — these depend on each other

