## Open Questions

> [!IMPORTANT]
> 1. **Translation API:** Should we use `googletrans` (free, offline) or the HuggingFace LLM for translation? `googletrans` is faster but may have rate limits for large texts.

> [!IMPORTANT]
> 2. **Multi-user scope:** Should the login system support:
>    - (A) Simple: Just username + password, notebooks fully private per user
>    - (B) Full: Username + password + ability to share notebooks with specific users + group chat visibility
>    - Current plan assumes option B.

> [!IMPORTANT]
> 3. **Guardrail strictness:** How strict should the query scope guardrail be?
>    - (A) Loose: Only block clearly harmful/off-topic queries
>    - (B) Strict: Only allow questions directly answerable from uploaded documents
>    - Current plan defaults to B with a toggle to switch off.

